19:T469,This is clearly a specific length variant (L4=305mm) of the Meril MonoMod modular revision hip stem system with 135° CCD angle. Internal evidence is consistent and provides technical specifications. The product represents a single implant class within a modular revision system. However, critical ambiguities exist: (1) Brand field is empty despite 'Meril' being manufacturer - needs confirmation if MonoMod is the brand or just product line; (2) Material is unspecified - revision stems are typically titanium alloy or cobalt-chrome, material specification is clinically critical; (3) No external verification available to confirm product existence or validate specifications; (4) Uncertain if L4 variant should be separate product page or part of consolidated MonoMod family page showing all length variants. Confidence reduced to 0.7 due to missing material data and lack of external verification. Manual review required to: confirm brand hierarchy, specify material composition, determine optimal page structure (individual vs consolidated variants), and validate technical specifications against manufacturer documentation.15:["$","$L18",null,{"product":{"product_name":"Meril MonoMod Revision Stem L4","product_name_display":"MonoMod Revision Stem L4","sku_code":"L4","product_family":"Meril MonoMod Revision Stem L4","product_family_display":"Meril MonoMod Revision Stem L4","slug":"meril-monomod-revision-stem-l4","images":[{"id":"19b9066fc36d","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c17bd504841ec9248cfabb/cover_6899289c.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Destiknee Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":208705,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:55:44.917719+00:00","source":"division_fallback","width":1600,"height":1600}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"agile-ortho/brochures/latitud-hip-system.pdf","seo_meta_title":"MonoMod Revision Stem L4 | Meril MonoMod Hip Revision Systems - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"MonoMod Revision St